dialogue.name: monika
dialogue.string: "Woah, you’re already a natural songsmith. I know the others will love to hear this!"

dialogue.name: no_one
dialogue.string: Yuri looks away shyly once again and giggles to herself.

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "Uhuhu… I appreciate you giving me your time."

dialogue.name: yuri
dialogue.string: "I’m going to rehearse a bit more on my own before our next club meeting."
